In the 21st century, a mystery unfurled for America. 1776 whispered through time as love marked the year 2011. On September 10, 2011, a firstborn prince arrived, a date bright as a crown. They called him Rafael Aman, a name carried by faith, hope, and peace. A young mother and a steadfast father held him as history held its breath. Great men grew older that day, but a greater story grew new. From Royal Oak dreams to ocean-spanning prayers, the nation felt a quiet tremor. God’s hand, some said, pressed gently on the clock and turned it toward mercy. The child’s cry braided 1776 with now, stitching liberty to love. Crowns are not always forged in gold; sometimes they are minted in purpose. And so a prince for the United States was born, to walk our time with light.

📚 Understanding Gematria

Telugu Gematria / తెలుగు గెమెట్రియా

English: Telugu Gematria assigns numerical values to Telugu letters. This ancient practice reveals hidden meanings and spiritual connections in Telugu literature and sacred texts.

తెలుగు: తెలుగు గెమెట్రియా తెలుగు అక్షరాలకు సంఖ్యా విలువలను కేటాయిస్తుంది. ఈ పురాతన అభ్యాసం తెలుగు సాహిత్యం మరియు పవిత్ర గ్రంథాలలో దాగిన అర్థాలను మరియు ఆధ్యాత్మిక సంబంధాలను వెల్లడిస్తుంది.

English Gematria

Gematria is the practice of assigning numerical values to letters, words, and phrases. In English Gematria, each letter (A=1, B=2, C=3... Z=26) has a specific value that reveals hidden meanings and divine connections between words with the same numerical total.

Hebrew Gematria / גימטריה עברית

English: Hebrew Gematria is the ancient practice of assigning numerical values to Hebrew letters. Each letter has a specific value (א=1, ב=2, ג=3...) used to find hidden connections in sacred texts.

עברית: גימטריה עברית היא תרגול עתיק של הקצאת ערכים מספריים לאותיות עבריות. לכל אות יש ערך ספציפי המשמש למציאת קשרים נסתרים בטקסטים קדושים.

Hindi Gematria / हिंदी गेमेट्रिया

English: Hindi Gematria assigns numerical values to Devanagari letters. This system reveals spiritual connections and hidden meanings in Sanskrit and Hindi texts.

हिंदी: हिंदी गेमेट्रिया देवनागरी अक्षरों को संख्यात्मक मान प्रदान करता है। यह प्रणाली संस्कृत और हिंदी ग्रंथों में आध्यात्मिक संबंधों और छुपे अर्थों को प्रकट करती है।

Arabic Gematria / علم الجمّل العربي

English: Arabic Gematria (Abjad) assigns numerical values to Arabic letters. This ancient system reveals mystical connections and hidden meanings in Quranic verses and Arabic texts.

العربية: علم الجمّل العربي (أبجد) يعطي قيماً عددية للحروف العربية. هذا النظام القديم يكشف الروابط الصوفية والمعاني الخفية في الآيات القرآنية والنصوص العربية.

Greek Gematria / Ελληνική Γεματρία

English: Greek Gematria (Isopsephy) assigns numerical values to Greek letters. Used in ancient times to find hidden meanings in religious and philosophical texts.

Ελληνικά: Η Ελληνική Γεματρία (Ισοψηφία) αποδίδει αριθμητικές αξίες στα ελληνικά γράμματα. Χρησιμοποιήθηκε στην αρχαιότητα για να βρει κρυφά νοήματα σε θρησκευτικά και φιλοσοφικά κείμενα.
